/-- **THE NIST ANCHOR for ML-DSA-65 verify**: on every one of the 15 NIST ACVP `ML-DSA-sigVer-FIPS204`
`tgId = 3` vectors (`tcId` 31-45), the Lean `verifyCore` returns exactly NIST's published `testPassed`
